sentences.english: Leo Blair was the first child born to a serving British prime minister for 150 years.
sentences.chinese: 這是150年來首個在唐寧街首相府出生的孩子。

sentences.english: There is private fury with Legg in Downing Street for rewriting the rules.
sentences.chinese: 但在唐寧街，仍然有人私下對萊格修改規定憤恨不已。

sentences.english: Brown at No. 10 for the past decade.
sentences.chinese: 過去10年裏，應笣髑布朗入住唐寧街10號。

sentences.english: Downing Street was packed with well-wishers and photographers when Thatcher arrived.
sentences.chinese: 當撒切爾到達的時候，唐寧街擠滿了祝賀者和攝影師。
